Bank of Korea Vows to Focus Policy on Growth and Price Stability

-- B y   W i l l i a m   S i m
-- 
2011-09-27T01:00:00Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-27/bank-of-korea-vows-to-focus-policy-on-growth-and-price-stability.html
The  Bank of Korea  said its monetary
policy will continue to focus on both securing  price stability 
and sustaining economic growth amid rising global uncertainties.  “We will manage monetary policy with more focus on firmly
securing price stability while sustaining solid economic growth
as we closely monitor economic and financial risks at home and
abroad,” the bank central said in a report prepared for its
parliamentary audit today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
William Sim in Seoul at 
